Nokia ovi suite is a computer program available for Microsoft Windows that allows nokia users to backup the contents of their phones to the PC, install maps on the phone, [[tethering]] (act as a modem to connect the computer to the Internet), updating the phone software, among other things. It is expected to be the replacement of [[Nokia PC Suite]] and is integrated with the [[Ovi (Nokia)|"ovi"]] brand of services.
